      <url>/jcxj/2022/09/21/go-jian-li-di-yi-ge-gong-cheng-ji-bian-liang-pei-zhi/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="1-环境变量问题"><a href="#1-环境变量问题" class="headerlink" title="1.环境变量问题"></a>1.环境变量问题</h1><p>在安装go编译器和goland的时候随手勾选添加到环境变量的选项即可</p><p>效果长这样</p><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/21/go-jian-li-di-yi-ge-gong-cheng-ji-bian-liang-pei-zhi/image-20220921204933709.png" class="" title="image-20220921204933709"><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/21/go-jian-li-di-yi-ge-gong-cheng-ji-bian-liang-pei-zhi/image-20220921204823272.png" class="" title="image-20220921204823272"><p>Path中的</p><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/21/go-jian-li-di-yi-ge-gong-cheng-ji-bian-liang-pei-zhi/image-20220921204854303.png" class="" title="image-20220921204854303"><h1 id="2-goland创建一个工程"><a href="#2-goland创建一个工程" class="headerlink" title="2.goland创建一个工程"></a>2.goland创建一个工程</h1><p><strong>file-setting</strong></p><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/21/go-jian-li-di-yi-ge-gong-cheng-ji-bian-liang-pei-zhi/image-20220921205126572.png" class="" title="image-20220921205126572"><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/21/go-jian-li-di-yi-ge-gong-cheng-ji-bian-liang-pei-zhi/image-20220921205144053.png" class="" title="image-20220921205144053"><p>在右上角 edit configuration或者 addconfiguration中配置下</p><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/21/go-jian-li-di-yi-ge-gong-cheng-ji-bian-liang-pei-zhi/image-20220921205343563.png" class="" title="image-20220921205343563"><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/21/go-jian-li-di-yi-ge-gong-cheng-ji-bian-liang-pei-zhi/image-20220921205314924.png" class="" title="image-20220921205314924"><p>正常new一个project然后在project目录下建立三个文件夹</p><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/21/go-jian-li-di-yi-ge-gong-cheng-ji-bian-liang-pei-zhi/image-20220921205103980.png" class="" title="image-20220921205103980"><h3 id="写一个代码"><a href="#写一个代码" class="headerlink" title="写一个代码"></a>写一个代码</h3><p>注意的是package需要些main而不是src</p><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/21/go-jian-li-di-yi-ge-gong-cheng-ji-bian-liang-pei-zhi/image-20220921205403275.png" class="" title="image-20220921205403275"><p><strong>成功运行</strong></p><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/21/go-jian-li-di-yi-ge-gong-cheng-ji-bian-liang-pei-zhi/image-20220921205430038.png" class="" title="image-20220921205430038">]]></content>
      
      
      
